author: Adam Savage’s Tested
description:
After poring over the details of the incredible Mondoshawan costume from The Fifth Element on his last visit to Propstore, Adam gets an audience with another iconic costume from the film: the distinctive police uniform of the film's future cops. We find this screen-matched costume in remarkable condition, with details and previously unseen functionality that Adam discovers for the first time!

Learn more about this prop and see more details at: https://propstoreauction.com/auctions/info/id/462
Adam Savage Meets The Fifth Element's Mondoshawan Costume: https://youtu.be/pf5dPrmBvwE

Shot by Josh Self and edited by Norman Chan
Music by Jinglepunks
